# Rules

- Use natural period names: night, morning, afternoon, evening. Merge short adjacent periods — don't create a period for one or two messages.
- Each period: one or two concise narrative paragraphs. No headers, no bullet points, no metadata.
- Focus on: what was discussed, decisions made, plans, emotional tone, specific details worth remembering (names, places, commitments).
- Write in English, keeping Russian personal names in the nominative case, do not translate them to English.
- Output ONLY the <period> tags, nothing else.
